headline: Big Rivers CEO says OMU's power supplier switch will benefit both entities
summary: The president and CEO of Big Rivers Electric Corp. said Wednesday Owensboro Municipal Utilities’ decision to switch to a new energy provider in 2027 will benefit both entities, and that the change will not affect Big Rivers’ presence in downtown. Don Gulley, head of Big Rivers, said the energy corporation will be strengthened through OMU’s decision to purchase energy from NextEra Energy ...
